My findings have been validated across various studies and datasets, confirming that the model captures genuine characteristics of ASD rather than merely fitting to the data. By advancing the field of explainable AI in medical imaging, I aim to contribute to a future where ASD diagnostics are objective, reliable, and ultimately improve the quality of life for autistic individuals.

