ugh review of the proposal will be conducted to ensure clarity, coherence, and completeness. The proposal will be reviewed by peers and mentors to refine it further.\n- **Revisions:** Based on feedback from peers and mentors, the proposal will be revised to address any issues or concerns. The final proposal will be well-structured, comprehensive, and compelling.\n\nBy following these steps, the research proposal will be well-structured, comprehensive, and compelling, providing a solid foundation for the research project."}

